  MSG_Kyu_03:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 2
      - text: "I'm the kind of guy who sees everything\nin his life through horse-tinted glasses.\n\nDid you know that some of the stables in\nHyrule have slightly different bridle and\nsaddle styles?\nI know of four for sure:\n\n\nWoodland Stable, Highland Stable,\nOutskirt Stable,"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\nand South Akkala Stable..."
  MSG_Kyu_03_1:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: "I know of four stables in Hyrule that have\nslightly different bridle and saddle styles:\n\nWoodland Stable, Highland Stable,\nOutskirt Stable,"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: " and South Akkala Stable."
  MSG_Kyu_04:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 2
      - text: "I love every little thing about horses.\nI love their fur, the way they smell,\ntheir bones even.\nSpeaking of bones, I once rode a horse\nmade of nothing but bones! No lie! It\nwas up in the snowy mountains.\nWas I scared, you ask? Nope. I could\nnever be scared of a horse.\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 1
            - 11
      - text: "That bony horse ran really well, and it\nwas actually a surprisingly comfortable\nride."
  MSG_Kyu_04_1:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 1
            - 11
      - text: "The horse made of bones that I rode up\nin the snowy mountains was surprisingly\ncomfortable to mount."
