          length: longer
      - text: "for a horse.\n\nBut it's not all bad. Gives me more time\nto talk about horses.\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: "I heard that there's something special\nnear Satori Mountain northwest of\nthe Great Plateau.\nTo the east of the mountain, you'll find\nSanidin Park Ruins, and near there...\nis a special horse fit for a king."
  Rest_01:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 2
      - text: "I'm bored and it's raining, so how\nabout I give you a little horse quiz.\n\nWhite horse..."
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: " Giant horse..."
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: " Mechanical\nhorse... "
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "Bone horse... "
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "Now,"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: " which of\nthese horses doesn't exist in this world?"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: "The answer will be revealed someday,\nsomewhere."
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
