      - text: "you'd best give up hope\nof hearing about anything other than\nhorses from me.\nGirls often talk dreamily about princes on\nwhite horses or some odd nonsense...\n\nBut I couldn't care less about some\nstuffy prince. Give me the white horse!\n\n"
