            - 0
            - 4
      - text: "You can't expect a horse to ride hard for\nyou if you don't have a meaningful\nconnection with it."
  RetMSG_Kyu_02:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 2
      - text: "I spend two-thirds of every day thinking\nabout horses"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: " and the remaining third\ndreaming about them.\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 6
      - text: "Hey, did you know wild horses will run\nfrom you if they sense you approaching?\nIt can be pretty frustrating.\nBut the ones that are hard to catch\nusually perform the best."
  RetMSG_Kyu_02_1:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: "Remember, wild horses that are quicker\nto run from you are generally the best\nperformers."
  RetMSG_Kyu_03:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 2
      - text: "If you came to ask me about\nHyrule Castle,"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: " you're barking up\nthe wrong tree.\nHorses,"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: " horses,"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: " horses.\nThat's all I care about.\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: "Finding and taming a wild horse is like\nadopting a new family member..."
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "\nthat you can sit on.\nOnce you register your horse companion\nat a stable,"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: " it'll always be by your side."
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\nForever. "
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: Unless it dies.
  RetMSG_Kyu_03_1:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: "Once you tame a wild horse, it becomes\nfamily."
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: " Register it at a stable to make it\nofficial."
  RetMSG_Kyu_04:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 2
      - text: "If you get me started about horses, you'll\nbe here for a while."
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: " I can go on about\nhorses longer than a horse's face.\nThis saddle fits my horse's back\nperfectly,"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: " and it also fits my rear end\nperfectly. I'm mighty happy with it.\nThis bridle is easy to grasp,"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: " and it's\npretty elastic, so it's easy to handle.\n\nWhen you register a wild horse at a\nstable,"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: " they'll fit it with a saddle and\na bridle.\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: "Well, that's all I have to say about that."
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\nDidn't go on as long as I thought I\nwould."
  RetMSG_Kyu_04_1:
    attributes: Npc_Road_035
    contents:
      - control:
